Package: robustscale
Title: Robust Ensemble Scale Estimation of Predictive Uncertainty
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dennis Alexis Valin", "Dittrich", 
           email = "davd@economicscience.net", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4438-8276"))
Description: Implements a high-performance, variance-weighted 
    ensemble of robust scale estimators. Optimized for uncertainty 
    quantification in small-sample regimes (n < 50) typically encountered 
    in causal machine learning and econometrics.
